reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice piece of furniture.
reviews.reviewText: Sturdy, attractive, functional and so quick and easy to assemble that I didn't even have time for a beer break!The power/charging outlet is a very convenient feature. It's the perfect size for a night stand. Well designed, with a shelf and three drawers. The fabric drawers are a lot sturdier than I had expected. Excellent value, my wife and I are on a very low fixed income and affordability is a big factor in all our purchase decisions.When I placed it by my wife's bed she said "Now that's a nice piece of furniture.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Heavy duty, sturdy and lite!
reviews.reviewText: Was a but worried that these drawers wont be sturdy enough, or if i pull out a drawer the whole thing moves. But I was completely wrong, nothing moves when pulling a drawer! Easy to assemble, high quality and plenty of space! The added electrical ports were a great touch. The touch of wood and fabric is what makes these drawers pretty good looking.One man job to put together, I highly recommend this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very nice nightstand!
reviews.reviewText: Love this nightstand overall! Fantastic piece to give some character to my college apartment bedroom.Assembly was smooth and easy, and it all looks and feels solid. The wood panels especially look very sharp (and slightly darker than they appeared online but I actually think they look like higher quality IRL than they do in the pictures). The power port functions and is so convenient! The drawers are thin and light but quite sturdy, I’m able to store plenty of office supplies, cleaning supplies, etc. Yes, it’s smaller than it looks in pictures online, but the product dimensions listed online are accurate, so just look to those if you’re curious about the true size.Only reason I give 4 stars instead of 5 is that when attaching the base frame pieces (5 and 6) to the top frame pieces (3 and 4), the instructions said to insert screws to hold the pieces together, but the “screw holes” are not threaded holes, they’re just open holes so the screws don’t have anything to thread into. Thankfully it didn’t matter because the base and top frame pieces actually slide together securely and there’s really no way for it to disassemble. Maybe this was just a minor defect with my specific nightstand?All in all, highly recommend this nightstand for the price. 100% worth it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty good for as cheap as it is
reviews.reviewText: This nightstand while being decently cheap also is very sturdy and nice especially with the charging station. Now I did want to have wood bins but that’s not going to happen at this price point. Either way the fabric bins do just fine and the two shelves are nice. I like having a top and bottom layer for more space. It was easy to assemble everything, very clear instructions with labels on each piece and bag. It came with tools as well to assemble it so that’s always a plus. So far very happy with it and love the look of rustic brown wood.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Bought two for the bedroom recently, and couldn’t be happier !! They arrived days earlier than expected, and was super easy to build. They give you everything you need to build it, and included spare bolts for that “just in case” moment that all of us have. Comes in different sizes and colors. We chose the 4 drawer, which is the perfect height for our bed. The drawers concerned me at first, but after putting them together, they turned out to be quite sturdy. Would highly recommend these for anyone wanting some quality nightstands.
